<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Your wife will be like a fruitful vine</para>

<para style="q1">in your house;</para>

<para style="q1">your children will be like olive plants</para>

<para style="q1">as they sit around your table.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Yes, indeed, the man will be blessed</para>

<para style="q1">who honors Yahweh.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />May Yahweh bless you from Zion;</para>

<para style="q1">may you see the prosperity of Jerusalem all the days of your life.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />May you live to see your children's children.</para>

<para style="q1">May peace be on Israel.</para>
